page.title: 07A day in the life of Ian
page.content: I wake up at 6.15 a.m and get up at 6.45 a.m . I get dressed at 6.55 a.m . I clean my teeth and have a wash at 7.07 a.m.At 7.22 a.m I comb my hair and then put on my shoes.Then I go outside and have a ride on my bike. Time 7.40 a.m.Then I put the bike away.Time 8.07 a.m.Then I go in the house and have breakfast.Time 8.10 a.m.I get to {school}at 8.40 a.m and start at 9.00 a.m to do maths and English.We have break at 10.40 a.m and do work again at 11.00 a.m until 12.00 noon.At 12.00 noon we have dinner and have break at 12.20 p.m.when we come in we might go out again to do long jump.After we have done that we work until 2.20 p.m.We come in at 2.40 p.m. and do written work until home time at 3.30 p.m.I play about until 6.00 p.m. teatime then more play until bed at 9.35 p.m.
